Their kinsmen the Levites were appointed for all the service of the tabernacle of the house of God. -- 1 chronicles 6:48
.
But Aaron and his sons offered on the altar of burnt offering and on the altar of incense, for all the work of the most holy place, and to make atonement for Israel, according to all that Moses the servant of God had commanded. -- 1 chronicles 6:49
.
