Now these are their settlements according to their camps within their borders. To the sons of Aaron of the families of the Kohathites (for theirs was the first lot), -- 1 chronicles 6:54
.
to them they gave Hebron in the land of Judah and its pasture lands around it; -- 1 chronicles 6:55
.
but the fields of the city and its villages, they gave to Caleb the son of Jephunneh. -- 1 chronicles 6:56
.
